sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant App as Mobile Prover
    participant Circuit as ZKP Circuit (planned)
    participant Output as Proof Artifact

    Note over App, Output: Circuit Logic: "Age > Threshold" (Range Check)

    %% Inputs
    App->>Circuit: Input: Private_Age [SECRET]
    activate App
    App->>Circuit: Input: Public_Threshold
    activate Circuit
    
    %% Constraints
    Note right of Circuit: Constraint 1:<br/>assert(Private_Age >= Public_Threshold)
    Circuit->>Circuit: Verify Mathematical Constraint
    
    Note right of Circuit: Constraint 2:<br/>assert(Signature_Valid == True)
    Circuit->>Circuit: Verify Issuer Signature (EdDSA)
    
    %% Output Generation
    alt Constraints Met
        Circuit-->>Output: Generate "Proof String" (hex)
        Output-->>App: Success
    else Constraints Failed
        Circuit-->>App: Error: Constraint Not Satisfied
    end
    deactivate Circuit
    deactivate App
    
    Note over App: The App now sends ONLY the<br/>Proof String to the Verifier.
